properties.script:
out0 = spark.sql(f"""
    SELECT
   '{Config.sourceSystem}' AS SRC_SYS_CD
, TRIM(MFGORDER.MFGORDERID) as MFG_ORDR_ID
, TRIM(MFGORDER.PRODUCTID) as PROD_ID
, CAST(NULL AS STRING) as ARMOUR_TYPE_CD
, CAST(NULL AS STRING) as BK_CASETTE_DSGN_TXT
, CAST(NULL AS STRING) as BK_CASETTE_DSGN_2_TXT
, CAST(NULL AS STRING) as BTCH_NUM
, TRIM(MFGORDER.BEGINPRODUCTBASEID) as BEG_PROD_BASE_ID
, TRIM(MFGORDER.BEGINPRODUCTID) as BEG_PROD_ID
, TRIM(MFGORDER.BILLOFPROCESSID) as BILL_OF_PRCS_ID
, TRIM(MFGORDER.BILLOFPROCESSBASEID) as BILL_OF_PRCS_BASE_ID
, CAST(NULL AS STRING) as BOM_BASE_ID
, CAST(NULL AS STRING) as BOM_ID
, CAST(NULL AS STRING) as CAVITY_FOIL_CD
, TRIM(MFGORDER.ETHCELLID) as CELL_ID
, INT(MFGORDER.CHANGECOUNT) as CHG_CNT
, TRIM(MFGORDER.CHANGESTATUSID) as CHG_STS_ID
, CAST(NULL AS STRING) as CNSTR_CD
, TRIM(MFGORDER.CONTAINERNUMBERINGRULEID) as CNTNR_NUMING_RULE_ID
, TRIM(MFGORDER.ETHCURRENTORDERSTATUSID) as CUR_ORDR_STS_ID
, TRIM(MFGORDER.DEFAULTLOT) as DFLT_LOT_NUM
, TRIM(MFGORDER.DEFAULTPUTAWAYSTOCKPOINT) as DFLT_PUTAWAY_STK_PT_NM
, CAST(NULL AS STRING) as DIFF_SUTURE_MATL_CD
, CAST(NULL AS INT) as DOC_CNT
, CAST(NULL AS STRING) as DOSSR_NUM
, TRIM(MFGORDER.ERPBOMID) as ERP_BOM_ID
, CAST(NULL AS STRING) as ERP_LOC_NM
, TRIM(MFGORDER.ERPROUTEBASEID) as ERP_RTE_BASE_ID
, TRIM(MFGORDER.ERPROUTEID) as ERP_RTE_ID
, CAST(NULL AS TIMESTAMP) as EXPN_DTTM
, CAST(NULL AS TIMESTAMP) as EXPN_2_DTTM
, CAST(MFGORDER.EXTERNALLYCONTROLLED as BOOLEAN ) as EXTR_CTL_IND
, CAST(NULL AS STRING) as FCTRY_ID
, CAST(MFGORDER.QTY AS DECIMAL(18,4)) as FNL_QTY
, CAST(NULL AS STRING) as FRN_CASETTE_DSGN_TXT
, CAST(NULL AS STRING) as FRN_CASETTE_DSGN_2_TXT
, CAST(NULL AS STRING) as GS1_CD
, CAST(MFGORDER.ETHHOLDERPPROCESSING as BOOLEAN ) as HOLD_ERP_PRCSG_IND
, TRIM(MFGORDER.ICONID) as ICON_ID
, TRIM(MFGORDER.ETHINTERFACECODE) as INTF_CD
, CAST(NULL AS BOOLEAN) as IS_CLSE_IND
, CAST(MFGORDER.ISFROZEN as BOOLEAN ) as IS_FRZN_IND
, CAST(NULL AS BOOLEAN) as IS_HOT_LOT_IND
, CAST(MFGORDER.ISKITTINGORDER as BOOLEAN ) as IS_KITTING_ORDR_IND
, CAST(NULL AS BOOLEAN) as IS_POP_CONV_IND
, CAST(MFGORDER.ISPREACTORSCHEDULEID as BOOLEAN ) as IS_PREACTOR_SCHD_IND
, CAST(NULL AS BOOLEAN) as IS_PRDTN_IND
, CAST(NULL AS BOOLEAN) as IS_SAP_ALT_ID_VLD_REQ_IND
, CAST(NULL AS BOOLEAN) as IS_VLD_SAP_BOM_ALT_ID_IND
, TRIM(MFGORDER.ETHJDEFIELD10) as JDE_FLD_10_TXT
, TRIM(MFGORDER.ETHJDEFIELD4) as JDE_FLD_4_TXT
, TRIM(MFGORDER.ETHJDEFIELD5) as JDE_FLD_5_TXT
, TRIM(MFGORDER.ETHJDEFIELD6) as JDE_FLD_6_TXT
, TRIM(MFGORDER.ETHJDEFIELD7) as JDE_FLD_7_TXT
, TRIM(MFGORDER.ETHJDEFIELD8) as JDE_FLD_8_TXT
, TRIM(MFGORDER.ETHJDEFIELD9) as JDE_FLD_9_TXT
, INT(MFGORDER.ETHJDELEANSEQUENCE) as LEAN_SEQ_NBR
, TRIM(MFGORDER.ETHLINEID) as LINE_ID
, CAST(NULL AS STRING) as LOC_ID
, Case when ETHJDELOTEXPIRATIONDATE = '0000000000' then CAST(null AS TIMESTAMP) else to_timestamp(left(MFGORDER.ETHJDELOTEXPIRATIONDATE ,14),\"yyyyMMddHHmmss\") end AS LOT_EXPN_DTTM
, CAST(NULL AS STRING) as MSTR_LOT_ID
, CAST(NULL AS STRING) as MSTR_LOT_NM
, CAST(NULL AS STRING) as MATL_COLOR_CD
, CAST(NULL AS TIMESTAMP) as MFG_DTTM
, CAST(NULL AS TIMESTAMP) as MFG_2_DTTM
, TRIM(MFGORDER.DESCRIPTION) as MFG_ORDR_DESC
, TRIM(MFGORDER.MFGORDERNAME) as MFG_ORDR_NM
, CAST(MFGORDER.QTY2 AS DECIMAL(18,4)) as FNL_2_QTY
, CAST(NULL AS STRING) as MRP_CTL_NM
, CAST(NULL AS STRING) as NEEDLE_MFR_NM
, CAST(NULL AS STRING) as NEEDLE_TYPE_CD
, TRIM(MFGORDER.NOTES) as NOTES_TXT
, TRIM(MFGORDER.CDOTYPEID) as OBJ_TYPE_ID
, TRIM(MFGORDER.ETHOPERATIONSCRAP) as OPR_SCRAP_VAL
, TRIM(MFGORDER.ORDERSTATUSID) as ORDR_STS_ID
, TRIM(MFGORDER.ORDERTYPEID) as ORDR_TYPE_ID
, Case when MFGORDER.PLANNEDCOMPLETIONDATE = '0000000000' then CAST(NULL AS TIMESTAMP) else to_timestamp(left(MFGORDER.PLANNEDCOMPLETIONDATE ,14),\"yyyyMMddHHmmss\") end AS PLAN_CMPLT_DTTM
, Case when MFGORDER.PLANNEDCOMPLETIONDATEGMT = '0000000000' then CAST(NULL AS TIMESTAMP) else to_timestamp(left(MFGORDER.PLANNEDCOMPLETIONDATEGMT ,14),\"yyyyMMddHHmmss\") end AS PLAN_CMPLT_GMT_DTTM
, Case when MFGORDER.PLANNEDSTARTDATE = '0000000000' then CAST(NULL AS TIMESTAMP) else to_timestamp(left(MFGORDER.PLANNEDSTARTDATE ,14),\"yyyyMMddHHmmss\") end AS PLAN_STRT_DTTM
, Case when MFGORDER.PLANNEDSTARTDATEGMT = '0000000000' then CAST(NULL AS TIMESTAMP) else to_timestamp(left(MFGORDER.PLANNEDSTARTDATEGMT ,14),\"yyyyMMddHHmmss\") end AS PLAN_STRT_GMT_DTTM
, CAST(NULL AS STRING) as PLNR_CD
, CAST(NULL AS BOOLEAN) as PRE_PRCSG_IND
, TRIM(MFGORDER.PRIORITYID) as PRIR_ID
, TRIM(MFGORDER.PRODUCTBASEID) as PROD_BASE_ID
, CAST(NULL AS STRING) as PROD_FMLY_ID
, CAST(NULL AS STRING) as PROD_TYPE_ID
, CAST(NULL AS STRING) as PROD_TYPE_2_ID
, CAST(NULL AS STRING) as PRDTN_SCHD_NM
, CAST(NULL AS STRING) as PRDTN_VERS_NUM
, Case when MFGORDER.RELEASEDATE = '0000000000' then CAST(NULL AS TIMESTAMP) else to_timestamp(left(MFGORDER.RELEASEDATE,8),\"yyyyMMdd\") end AS RLSE_DTTM
, Case when MFGORDER.RELEASEDATEGMT = '0000000000' then CAST(NULL AS TIMESTAMP) else to_timestamp(left(MFGORDER.RELEASEDATEGMT ,14),\"yyyyMMddHHmmss\") end AS RLSE_GMT_DTTM
, TRIM(MFGORDER.REPORTINGFACTORYID) as RPTG_FCTRY_ID
, CAST(NULL AS STRING) as RESV_NUM
, CAST(NULL AS BOOLEAN) as RESORBABLE_IND
, CAST(NULL AS STRING) as SAP_ALT_ID
, CAST(NULL AS TIMESTAMP) as SCHD_STRT_DTTM
, TRIM(MFGORDER.ETHSMR1DESCRIPTION) as SMR_1_DESC
, TRIM(MFGORDER.ETHSMR1) as SMR_1_NUM
, TRIM(MFGORDER.ETHSMR2DESCRIPTION) as SMR_2_DESC
, TRIM(MFGORDER.ETHSMR2) as SMR_2_NUM
, CAST(NULL AS STRING) as STERILIZATION_SPEC_CD
, CAST(NULL AS STRING) as STK_TYPE_CD
, CAST(NULL AS STRING) as SUTURE_SIZE_VAL
, CAST(NULL AS INT) as SUTURES_PER_FOIL_NBR
, CAST(MFGORDER.ETHJDEQTYTOTRANSFER AS DECIMAL(18,4)) as TO_TFR_QTY
, CAST(NULL AS STRING) as TRACEABL_INFO_TXT
, TRIM(MFGORDER.UOMID) as UOM_ID
, TRIM(MFGORDER.UOM2ID) as UOM_2_ID
, CAST(NULL AS BOOLEAN) as VLD_OVRD_IND
, CAST(NULL AS STRING) as VAL_STREM_TXT
, TRIM(MFGORDER.WIPMSGDEFMGRID) as WIP_MSG_DEF_MGR_ID
, TRIM(MFGORDER.ISWORKFLOWID) as WRKF_ID
, CAST(NULL AS INT) as YR_PRODCD_NBR
FROM {Config.sourceDatabase}.MFGORDER as MFGORDER
Where MFGORDER._deleted_ = 'F'  
 
""")
